    <title>Arch基本使用</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2024/02/07/arch-ji-ben-shi-yong/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2024/02/07/arch-ji-ben-shi-yong/</id>
    <published>2024-02-07T05:22:58.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-07-25T14:25:08.202Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>我的<a href="https://github.com/myself-jy/dotfile">仓库</a></p><h1 id="基本桌面安装"><a href="#基本桌面安装" class="headerlink" title="基本桌面安装"></a>基本桌面安装</h1><p>禁用<code>reflector</code>服务，避免其自己更新镜像源</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl stop reflector.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>测试网络环境。无线网络需手动开启网络</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">iwctl # 进入交互式命令行</span><br><span class="line">device list # 列出无线网卡设备名，比如无线网卡看到叫 wlan0</span><br><span class="line">station wlan0 scan # 扫描网络</span><br><span class="line">station wlan0 get-networks # 列出所有 wifi 网络</span><br><span class="line">station wlan0 connect wifi-name # 进行连接，注意这里无法输入中文。回车后输入密码即可</span><br><span class="line">exit # 连接成功后退出</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>若找不到设备可能是网卡没有驱动，使用有线网络安装<br>更新镜像源</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>全部删掉，替换成<a href="https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/help/archlinux.html">中科大镜像源</a>，然后更新软件包索引</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -Syy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>archinstall</code>开始安装<br>注意：文件系统推荐传统ext4格式；自己用户默认给su权限，可以避免后续麻烦；可以最小安装，或者也可选桌面和xorg安装，我这选xorg安装；驱动的话amd&#x2F;intel选开源驱动，英伟达选专有驱动；音频推荐pipewire；网络选择networkmanager；时区选择上海。<br>重启<br>先安装Neovim<br>使用Arch Linux CN 源</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nvim /etc/pacman.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>文末添加</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[archlinuxcn]</span><br><span class="line">Server = https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/archlinuxcn/$arch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更新源</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -Syyu</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装 archlinuxcn-keyring 包以导入 GPG key</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S archlinuxcn-keyring</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置locale</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nvim /etc/locale.gen</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>去掉<code>zh_CN.UTF-8 UTF-8</code>前的注释符号</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo locale-gen</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装基本环境</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S alacritty ＃终端</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S i3-gaps　＃i3-gaps</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S rofi＃起动器</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S polybar　　#顶栏</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S sddm     #dm</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S feh   #壁纸工具</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S picom   #混成器</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>开启sddm</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo systemctl enable sddm</span><br><span class="line">sudo systemctl start sddm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>登录后先选默认设置，而后按下win+enter，就能看见终端了<br>可以看看配置</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd ~/.config/i3</span><br><span class="line">nvim config</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>新增部分配置</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#启动picom</span><br><span class="line">exec --no-startup-id picom -b</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#使用feh设置壁纸，注意壁纸文件必须存在且路径正确</span><br><span class="line">exec --no-startup-id feh --bg-scale ~/zocoxx/wallpaper.jpeg</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#去除窗口的标题栏，有利有弊，好处是窗口少了额头，坏处是去除标题栏之后部分窗口无法进行鼠标拖动</span><br><span class="line">for_window [class=&quot;^.*&quot;] border pixel 0</span><br><span class="line">#设置边框为1像素</span><br><span class="line">new_window pixel 1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>对照注释都能看懂，先把他上面的依赖全装好，不建议你照搬下面代码，而是你自己对着每行查arch把包装好，如果有可选安装项可以自己看情况安装，像<code>python-pip</code>啥的就顺便装上就行。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S i3status　dex adobe-source-code-pro-fonts xss-lock network-manager-applet</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>把起动器换成rofi</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nvim ~/.config/i3/config</span><br><span class="line">bindsym $mod+d exec --no-startup-id rofi -show drun #win+d可以启动rofi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>把rofi的drun打开</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd ~/.config &amp;&amp; mkdir rofi &amp;&amp; cd rofi</span><br><span class="line">nvim config.rasi </span><br><span class="line">configuration &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  show-icons:         true;</span><br><span class="line">  modi: &quot;window,drun,ssh,run&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装基本桌面环境</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S ntfs-3g # 使系统可以识别 NTFS 格式的硬盘</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S dolphin thunar #文件管理工具</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S adobe-source-han-serif-cn-fonts wqy-zenhei # 安装几个开源中文字体。一般装上文泉驿就能解决大多 wine 应用中文方块的问题</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S noto-fonts noto-fonts-cjk noto-fonts-emoji noto-fonts-extra # 安装谷歌开源字体及表情</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S firefox # 安装火狐</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S ark # 压缩软件。在 dolphin 中可用右键解压压缩包</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S ristretto # 图片查看器</span><br><span class="line">sudo pacman -S vlc #视频播放器</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装输入法，这里推荐rime，个人基于fcitx5安装</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S fcitx5 fcitx5-qt fcitx5-gtk fcitx5-configtool fcitx5-rime</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>而后写入用户环境变量</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nvim ~/.pam_environment</span><br><span class="line">INPUT_METHOD DEFAULT=fcitx5</span><br><span class="line">GTK_IM_MODULE DEFAULT=fcitx5</span><br><span class="line">QT_IM_MODULE DEFAULT=fcitx5</span><br><span class="line">XMODIFIERS DEFAULT=\@im=fcitx5</span><br><span class="line">SDL_IM_MODULE DEFAULT=fcitx</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>现在在i3配置中添加一行启动fcitx5</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">exec_always --no-startup-id fcitx5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>而后打开fcitx5-configtool，把rime添加进去，作为默认输入法，重启。<br>开启aur支持</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S paru</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="进一步配置"><a href="#进一步配置" class="headerlink" title="进一步配置"></a>进一步配置</h1><h2 id="polybar设置及启动"><a href="#polybar设置及启动" class="headerlink" title="polybar设置及启动"></a>polybar设置及启动</h2><p>创建目录并设置配置文件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir ~/.config/polybar</span><br><span class="line">cp /etc/polybar/config.ini ~/.config/polybar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>要在启动i3wm之后默认启动polybar，需要有个启动脚本，文件名称、路径及内容如下</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># ~/.config/polybar/launch.sh</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#!/bin/bash</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 终端可能已经有在运行的实例</span><br><span class="line">killall -q polybar</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 等待进程被终止</span><br><span class="line">while pgrep -u $UID -x polybar &gt;/dev/null; do sleep 1; done</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 运行Polybar，使用默认的配置文件路径 ~/.config/polybar/config.ini</span><br><span class="line">polybar example &amp;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">echo &quot;Polybar launched...&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后给与启动脚本可执行权限</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">chmod +x ~/.config/polybar/launch.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后i3wm配置文件新加一行</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">exec --no-startup-id ~/.config/polybar/launch.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重启即可看到顶栏。记得注释掉i3配置文件中的i3-bar</p><h2 id="picom"><a href="#picom" class="headerlink" title="picom"></a>picom</h2><p>配置文件</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir ~/.config/picom/</span><br><span class="line">cp /etc/xdg/picom.conf ~/.config/picom/picom.conf</span><br><span class="line">nvim ~/.config/picom/picom.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在i3的配置文件中加入命令配置开机自启动</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">exec_always --no-startup-id picom -b</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>$mod+shift+r</code>重启i3即可<br>具体配置可以参考picom官方文档</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
